OL,3,CCompany fined #285,000 after worker
OL,4,Cdies during construction at university
OL,6,FA company has been fined more than
OL,7,F#285,000 and sentenced after a 62-year-
OL,8,Fold fell 10 metres to the ground and
OL,9,Fdied while working.
OL,11,FIgor Malka died and Edmund Vispulskis
OL,12,Fsuffered injuries to his spine and
OL,13,Fbroken ribs, before spending seven
OL,14,Fweeks in a neck brace.
OL,16,FMr Vispulskis also needed pins to be
OL,17,Finserted in his pelvis and thigh.
OL,19,FHow did this happen?
