OL,3,CCompany fined #285,000 after worker
OL,4,Cdies during construction at university
OL,6,FMr Malka and Mr Vispulskis were in a
OL,7,Fscissor lift while applying some
OL,8,Fmaterial to a new engineering hall at
OL,9,Fthe University of Birmingham on 7
OL,10,FJanuary 2020.
OL,12,FThe pair were constructing a new
OL,13,Funiversity facility.
OL,15,FThey fell roughly 10 metres when their
OL,16,Fscissor lift was pushed over by a
OL,17,Fnearby crane, which was being used to
OL,18,Fmove hydraulic equipment that had been
OL,19,Fdelivered by a lorry.
