OL,3,CCompany fined #285,000 after worker
OL,4,Cdies during construction at university
OL,6,FThe Health and Safety Executive (HSE)
OL,7,Finvestigated the fall and prosecuted
OL,8,FBalfour Beatty, giving them a fine on
OL,9,FMonday 16 September.
OL,11,FBalfour Beatty was the main contractor
OL,12,Fwhile the National Buried
OL,13,FInfrastructure Facility was being
OL,14,Fbuilt at the University of Birmingham.
OL,16,FThe HSE investigation found the
OL,17,Fincident could have been prevented if
OL,18,FBalfour Beatty introduced better
OL,19,Fcontrols and put in place better
OL,20,Fcommunication between contractors.
